reviews.text: Very average all day breakfast and coffee. There are a few vegetarian options. Good location and not expensive.

This cafe located at the lowest floor in K11, the fastest way to go there is leaving at TST MTR Exit N, not the front doors of K11. This cafe characterised by coffee and alcohol cross over, must try their special drinks! May need reservation on weekends night, mostly full around 7 ~8 pm. They have vege all day breakfast which I like the most. The pasta was also great. The size of the waffle is huge and tasty too!
Services are really ....... have a very big room for improvement. Especially the attitude and tone. Coffee is normal. Dessert can be neglected.
Food was good. A little expensive though.

Haven't had a legit meal like this before. Their coffee drinks are really good. I went there with a friend and we ordered the 2 people set meal. The set meal is enough to make you full. You got to choose a salad, a sandwich, a plate of pasta, and 2 cups of drinks and 2 pieces of cheesecakes. Their food is really awesome and tasty! I really love their spaghetti with green apple, asparagus and pine nuts in pesto sauce. Strongly recommend this dish! I would love to go there again!

reviews.text: 咖啡不錯👍🏼

叫咗個忌廉三文魚意粉同埋香草汁蘆筍雞肉意粉。 餐飲嘅名稱我唔記得，淨係記得一杯係花生味，一杯係熱情果味咖啡。

花生本身配上咖啡就係絕配， 所以呢杯花生咖啡絕對推介！
意粉都煮得唔錯， 煙韌彈牙。

黃金週嘅尖沙咀依舊一樣多人。
唔想排隊食飯，晚上九點鐘食咩好？
每次經過呢間牧羊人都係食飽落地鐵站先醒起，其仔幾間都試過晒，係爭呢一間未試。
其實想飲咖啡，但又太晚，下次lunch或tea再黎品嚐下。
食左兩樣好穩陣嘅dishes。拿破崙辣肉腸意粉，做得也幾出色，味道剛好。三文魚凱撒salad好味，唔會太多醬汁好heavy。
至於一行入黎，serve我嘅waiter感覺唔太想做⋯好似阻佢收工咁。呢樣可以改善下會更好。
Very average all day breakfast and coffee. There are a few vegetarian options. Good location and not expensive.
